\c 30
\p
\v 1 The word of the LORD came again unto me, saying, 
\v 2 Son of man, prophesy and say, Thus saith the Lord GOD; Howl ye, Woe worth
the day 
\v 3 For the day \add is\add* near, even the day of the LORD \add is
