\v 15 And one lamb out of the flock, out of two hundred, out of the fat
pastures of Israel; for a meat offering, and for a burnt offering, and for
peace offerings, to make reconciliation for them, saith the Lord GOD. 
\v 16 All the people of the land shall give this oblation for the prince in
Israel. 
\v 17 And it shall be the prince’s part \add to give\add* burnt offerings, and
