\v 18 Thus saith the Lord GOD; In the first \add month,\add* in the first 
\add day\add* of the month, thou shalt take a young bullock without blemish,
and cleanse the sanctuary: 
\v 19 And the priest shall take of the blood of the sin offering, and put 
\add it\add* upon the posts of the house, and upon the four corners of the
settle of the altar, and upon the posts of the gate of the inner court. 
\v 20 And so thou shalt do the seventh \add day\add* of the month for every
